command.text: M82 ; Set absolute mode for extruder
M150 ; Turn off all the lights
M84 ; Disable steppers, resetting the Z axis
G4 P500 ; Wait half a second for the Z axis to settle
M92 A8.88888 B8.88888 C8.88888 ; Rotational heads degrees per step
G28 Y F300; Home Y (bringing it to front of bed)
G28 Z F300; Home Z once we know its at Y0 (and in a safe place)
G28 X F300; Home X (after Y is safe)
G0 Z29.5 F800; Move Z back to zero (X moves it to safe position)
G92 A0 B0; Reset machine coordinates to zero.
M150 S0 I0 B75; LED light show
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
M150 S0 B255; LED light show
M260 B26; Continuous Conversion Mode, 16 bit, Channel 1, Gain x4
M260 B58; Continuous Conversion Mode, 16 bit, Channel 2, Gain x4
M150 S1 B{DoubleValue} P{DoubleValue} R{DoubleValue} U{DoubleValue}
M150 S0 B{DoubleValue} P{DoubleValue} R{DoubleValue} U{DoubleValue}
